Class FormEncodedBodyBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.http.FormEncodedBodyBuilder

  • public final class FormEncodedBodyBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class to create RequestBody objects that are x-www-url-form-encoded. Modeled after OkHttp's FormEncodingBuilder class.
